info.headline: High Wind Warning issued October 26 at 1:28PM MDT until October 27 at 12:00AM MDT by NWS Cheyenne
info.description: ...HIGH WIND WARNING REMAINS IN EFFECT UNTIL MIDNIGHT MDT TONIGHT... * WHAT...West winds 30 to 40 mph with gusts up to 60 mph expected. * WHERE...Central Carbon County, North Snowy Range Foothills and Upper North Platte River Basin. * WHEN...From 3 PM Today to midnight tonight. * IMPACTS...Travel could be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles on I-80.
info.instruction: People should avoid being outside in forested areas and around trees and branches. Use caution if you must drive.
